commit message:
Committing version 8264.1 as released.

Cope with orientation change gracefully, fixing some crashes.

Fix old items staying in Game Type menu.

Allow removal of a broken saved state.

Add first-time welcome dialog.

Import more cursor functionality from James Harvey's Palm port.

Fix line thickness in Solo (fix is now applied upstream).

Anti-alias straight lines and text.

Add email/website options to Help menu.
